"""
UIC Project Dashboard — Python GUI Application
================================================
Connects to CRC Oracle Data Warehouse to visualize UIC project data.
Features:
  1) Multi-select project picker with search
  2) Well list table with key attributes
  3) Injection history chart (water, steam, gas)
  4) Production history chart (oil, water, gas)
  5) Cumulative injection & production chart
  6) Well map (State Plane coordinates, colored by purpose/status)

Requirements:
  pip install oracledb pandas matplotlib

Usage:
  python uic_dashboard.py
"""

